\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4.6}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {Agent:} The agent is initialized with the tools, the memory, and the LLM. The agent decides what and when to use for each query. \textbf  {Memory:} Holds the entire conversation history and passes it as chat history to the agent. It is updated automatically by the agent after each turn. \textbf  {Tools:} Two custom tool functions are used to extract the patient name and then call the retriever filtering by that name.}}{72}{figure.caption.75}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:SystemA}{{4.6}{72}{\textbf {Agent:} The agent is initialized with the tools, the memory, and the LLM. The agent decides what and when to use for each query. \textbf {Memory:} Holds the entire conversation history and passes it as chat history to the agent. It is updated automatically by the agent after each turn. \textbf {Tools:} Two custom tool functions are used to extract the patient name and then call the retriever filtering by that name}{figure.caption.75}{}}
